####Simple config information for IIS#########################


##If you deploy a new .NET app you will need to add teh app pool user to the security of the folder

##deploy an app called dnn the app pool identity will be called 'dnn' unless you change it

##right click on the folder select the security tab in give IIS AppPool\dnn at least modify rights to the folder
###Make certain you are point to the local machine if you are on a domain joined system with the above command

###Or ICACLS
ICACLS d:\web\dnn /grant "IIS AppPool\dnn":F /t(for recursive)
